userPromptTemplate:
Generate a 'Listen and Repeat' set for TOEFL Speaking (2026 new format).

Difficulty: {{difficulty}}

Requirements:
- Generate exactly 7 sentences
- Topics: campus life, daily routines, academic activities, social situations
- Each sentence: 8-15 words
- Sentences should be natural spoken English (not overly formal)
- Vary sentence structure: statements, questions, suggestions
- CEFR level: Module1=B1-B2, Module2Easy=A2-B1, Module2Hard=B2-C1

Respond with this exact JSON structure:
{
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "text": "string — the complete sentence to display and then hide",
      "wordCount": 10
    }
  ]
}
